>>Michael stays seated during meals after his father frowns and glares at him every time he stands up.<<

( ) Reinforcement {{ Try Again }}
(x) Punishment    {{ Correct }}

[explanation]
Glaring makes Michael less likely to stand up, so this is punishment.
[/explanation]
]]></MarkupProblem>

